text: Raymond Michael Kethledge (born December 11, 1966) is an American judge. He is the United States Circuit Judge of the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit. He is a former law clerk for Associate Justice Anthony Kennedy of the Supreme Court of the United States. Kethledge is on President Donald Trump's list of potential Supreme Court justices. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Raymond Kethledge at the Biographical Directory of Federal Judges, a public domain publication of the Federal Judicial Center. * White House Profile Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:American judges Category:Lawyers from Michigan Category:Lawyers from New Jersey Category:Politicians from New Jersey Category:Politicians from Michigan Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:People from Summit, New Jersey
